transArray.content: I have lived here several times, and many stories have happened here, Sanyuan Bridge, Phoenix City, Zuojiazhuang. People come and go, the tide ebbs and flows, meeting by chance. The environment and facilities are very good. The front desk is also a small bar. Watching people chatting here is very lifelike. The chopped pepper fish head in nearby Xiang'ai is not bad, and there are several interesting restaurants.
